article.headline: Obioha puts up 21 as Niagara defeats Manhattan 81-67

images.name: Niagara Purple Eagles vs. Manhattan Jaspers: Full Highlights
images.caption: Niagara Purple Eagles vs. Manhattan Jaspers: Full Highlights

article.linkText: Obioha puts up 21 as Niagara defeats Manhattan 81-67
article.story: RIVERDALE, N.Y. -- — Harlan Obioha had 21 points in Niagara's 81-67 victory against Manhattan on Friday night. Obioha also contributed 16 rebounds for the Purple Eagles (5-8, 1-2 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Braxton Bayless added 20 points while going 8 of 12 and 4 of 4 from the free throw line, and he also had seven assists. Kwane Marble II had 11 points and shot 4 of 5 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line. Shaquil Bender scored 30 points and made five 3-pointers for the Jaspers (4-8, 1-2). Seydou Traore added 11 points and six rebounds for Manhattan. Briggs McClain also had nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
